<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-32">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    This Privacy Policy describes how OKPanel collects, uses, and discloses your information when you use our website. OKPanel is committed to protecting your privacy. If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
  <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    OKPanel is a static website and does not directly collect any personal identifying information from its visitors. We do not use cookies, trackers, or any other mechanisms to collect data about your browsing behavior or personal details.
  </p>
  <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    We use a simple, privacy-focused analytics service that collects anonymized, aggregated data such as page views and general geographic location (country level). This data cannot be used to identify individual users and is solely for understanding overall site traffic patterns.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    Since we do not collect personal identifying information, we do not use it for any purpose. The anonymized analytical data is used strictly for improving the performance and content of our website.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
  <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    Given that OKPanel does not collect or store personal user data, the risk of data breaches involving personal information is eliminated. We maintain appropriate security measures for our website hosting to protect against unauthorized access to or alteration of site data.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
  <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through the support link on our website.
  </p>
</main>
